      "text": "hence each space would have their own root and it cant change anything outside the space. this is \nmulti tenancy, and multi-tenancy is core feature of docker container.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "hence each space would have their own root and it cant change anything outside the space. this is \nmulti tenancy, and multi-tenancy is core feature of docker container.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2IIGbrxt4vjhDzDmnime-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1015.1690145463419,
      "y": 66903.51271455291,
      "width": 1199,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bjo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 496146011,
      "version": 629,
      "versionNonce": 299728654,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777685646398,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. VM is also a running process, To setup a VM we need a ISO file or we also call it as image file, similar\n    to this for containers also we need a image file. But both images are different bcx VM image has all the\n    kernels and Application softwares utility, binary everything but container image is bare set of binaries\n    if we want to install any applicatoin on top of it or repack that is a different case but otherwise it is\n    a minimal set of binaries.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. VM is also a running process, To setup a VM we need a ISO file or we also call it as image file, similar\n    to this for containers also we need a image file. But both images are different bcx VM image has all the\n    kernels and Application softwares utility, binary everything but container image is bare set of binaries\n    if we want to install any applicatoin on top of it or repack that is a different case but otherwise it is\n    a minimal set of binaries.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "D8o_j1JMFy96YejLj7FX1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1018.2510457963419,
      "y": 67089.04396455291,
      "width": 572,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bjr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1602654997,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 604520658,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777685646398,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Container is running process, Is image is a process?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Container is running process, Is image is a process?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Jx8wwqd19tfFn0ZmwEuj2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1066.954170796342,
      "y": 67126.93458955291,
      "width": 605,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bjs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1965190677,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 808873294,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777685646398,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "NO, ISO or image both are files. not a running process.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NO, ISO or image both are files. not a running process.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KgDms1EUtfidtIlX2m6aT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1001.4697957963419,
