      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777685646399,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "when we have converted to tar file and send that to other people or other system, using this tar file\nthey actually need to create a container from it or a image from it that is why we are creating to a tar\nfile",
