      "text": "Q Research find a dockerfile in whihc 3 stages are used, see that and try to understand.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q Research find a dockerfile in whihc 3 stages are used, see that and try to understand.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vcvuhXqBoK6MR_ex0_7Hm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1640.949505507995,
      "y": 97187.17947946498,
      "width": 572,
      "height": 975,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bp7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2056529508,
      "version": 172,
      "versionNonce": 1154854610,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777685646399,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🚀 What You’re Doing\n🧱 Stage 1 → Builder\n\nFROM node:18 AS builder\n\n\nInstalls dependencies\nBuilds your app (npm run build)\nProduces static files (React/Vite → /build or /dist)\n\n🌐 Stage 2 → Production (Nginx)\n\nFROM nginx:alpine\n\nTakes only built files\nServes them via Nginx\n\n✅ Key Benefits\n1. 🪶 Smaller Image Size\nNode image ≈ 300MB+\nNginx alpine ≈ 20–30MB\n\n👉 Final image contains:\n\n❌ No Node.js\n❌ No npm\n❌ No source code\n✔ Only static files\n\n➡️ Massive size reduction\n\n2. 🔐 Better Security\nNo build tools in final image\nLess attack surface\n\n👉 Hackers can’t:\n\nRun npm\nAccess source code easily",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🚀 What You’re Doing\n🧱 Stage 1 → Builder\n\nFROM node:18 AS builder\n\n\nInstalls dependencies\nBuilds your app (npm run build)\nProduces static files (React/Vite → /build or /dist)\n\n🌐 Stage 2 → Production (Nginx)\n\nFROM nginx:alpine\n\nTakes only built files\nServes them via Nginx\n\n✅ Key Benefits\n1. 🪶 Smaller Image Size\nNode image ≈ 300MB+\nNginx alpine ≈ 20–30MB\n\n👉 Final image contains:\n\n❌ No Node.js\n❌ No npm\n❌ No source code\n✔ Only static files\n\n➡️ Massive size reduction\n\n2. 🔐 Better Security\nNo build tools in final image\nLess attack surface\n\n👉 Hackers can’t:\n\nRun npm\nAccess source code easily",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iWqdSuZnq0HH9tVMeoEYX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1492.601849257995,
      "y": 98330.34744821498,
      "width": 1067,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
