      "versionNonce": 1600436682,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777771599387,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1 DSA -> daily 1:30 hour(revision)\n2 GenAI -> End then revision in 3 days(revision)\n3 AWS -> daily 1 hour\n4 LLD -> daily 30 minute(revision)\n5 HLD -> daily 30 minute(revision)\n6 SQL -> end then revision in 3 days\n7 Python -> end then revision in 3 days\n8 Django -> end then revision in 3 days\n9 HR   -> daily 15 minute(revision)\n10 Docker & Linux -> 30 minute daily(revision)\n11 Rahul -> 1 hour daily\n12 Resume -> daily 1 hour\n13 Job Apply -> daily 1 hour\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 DSA -> daily 1:30 hour(revision)\n2 GenAI -> End then revision in 3 days(revision)\n3 AWS -> daily 1 hour\n4 LLD -> daily 30 minute(revision)\n5 HLD -> daily 30 minute(revision)\n6 SQL -> end then revision in 3 days\n7 Python -> end then revision in 3 days\n8 Django -> end then revision in 3 days\n9 HR   -> daily 15 minute(revision)\n10 Docker & Linux -> 30 minute daily(revision)\n11 Rahul -> 1 hour daily\n12 Resume -> daily 1 hour\n13 Job Apply -> daily 1 hour\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
